{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":739,"text":"So today's top chef class is in how to rob a bank,"},{"time":4534,"text":"and it's clear that the general public needs guidance,"},{"time":8819,"text":"because the average bank robbery nets"},{"time":11692,"text":"only 7,500 dollars."},{"time":14230,"text":"Rank amateurs who know nothing"},{"time":16200,"text":"about how to cook the books."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18539,"text":"The folks who know, of course,"},{"time":20599,"text":"run our largest banks,"},{"time":22390,"text":"and in the last go-around,"},{"time":24908,"text":"they cost us over 11 trillion dollars."},{"time":29144,"text":"That's what 11 trillion looks like."},{"time":31561,"text":"That's how many zeros?"},{"time":33108,"text":"And cost us over 10 million jobs as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36544,"text":"So our task is to educate ourselves"},{"time":39195,"text":"so that we can understand"},{"time":40403,"text":"why we have these recurrent,"},{"time":42853,"text":"intensifying financial crises,"},{"time":44930,"text":"and how we can prevent them in the future."},{"time":48125,"text":"And the answer to that is"},{"time":50515,"text":"that we have to stop epidemics of control fraud."},{"time":54921,"text":"Control fraud is what happens"},{"time":56870,"text":"when the people who control,"},{"time":58690,"text":"typically a CEO,"},{"time":60415,"text":"a seemingly legitimate entity,"},{"time":62988,"text":"use it as a weapon to defraud."},{"time":65244,"text":"And these are the weapons of mass destruction"},{"time":68839,"text":"in the financial world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70939,"text":"They also follow in finance a particular strategy,"},{"time":75669,"text":"because the weapon of choice in finance"},{"time":78041,"text":"is accounting,"},{"time":79511,"text":"and there is a recipe for accounting"},{"time":83405,"text":"control fraud, and how it occurs."},{"time":85735,"text":"And we discovered this recipe"},{"time":87368,"text":"in quite an odd way that I'll\ncome back to in a moment."},{"time":90062,"text":"First ingredient in the recipe: grow like crazy;"},{"time":94039,"text":"second, by making or buying really crappy loans,"},{"time":99077,"text":"but loans that are made at a very high interest rate"},{"time":102560,"text":"or yield;"},{"time":104038,"text":"three, while employing extreme leverage --"},{"time":106270,"text":"that just means a lot of debt --"},{"time":107985,"text":"compared to your equity;"},{"time":109219,"text":"and four, while providing only trivial loss reserves"},{"time":113239,"text":"against the inevitable losses."},{"time":115423,"text":"If you follow those four simple steps,"},{"time":119089,"text":"and any bank can follow them,"},{"time":121390,"text":"then you are mathematically guaranteed"},{"time":123898,"text":"to have three things occur."},{"time":126088,"text":"The first thing is"},{"time":127648,"text":"you will report record bank profits --"},{"time":131012,"text":"not just high, record."},{"time":133523,"text":"Two, the CEO will immediately\nbe made incredibly wealthy"},{"time":138780,"text":"by modern executive compensation."},{"time":141676,"text":"And three, farther down the road,"},{"time":144546,"text":"the bank will suffer catastrophic losses"},{"time":147607,"text":"and will fail unless it is bailed out."},{"time":150803,"text":"And that's a hint as to how"},{"time":154543,"text":"we discovered this recipe,"},{"time":156279,"text":"because we discovered it\nthrough an autopsy process."},{"time":160355,"text":"During the savings and loan debacle in 1984,"},{"time":165267,"text":"we looked at every single failure,"},{"time":167722,"text":"and we looked for common characteristics,"},{"time":170139,"text":"and we discovered this recipe was common"},{"time":174398,"text":"to each of these frauds."},{"time":176712,"text":"In other words, a coroner could find these things"},{"time":179790,"text":"because this is a fatal recipe"},{"time":182650,"text":"that will destroy the banks"},{"time":184074,"text":"as well as the economy."},{"time":186165,"text":"And it also turns out to be precisely"},{"time":189678,"text":"what could have stopped this crisis,"},{"time":191940,"text":"the one that cost us 11 trillion dollars"},{"time":194462,"text":"just in the household sector,"},{"time":196398,"text":"that cost us 10 million jobs,"},{"time":198502,"text":"was the easiest financial crisis by far"},{"time":201956,"text":"to have avoided completely"},{"time":204427,"text":"if we had simply learned the lessons"},{"time":206499,"text":"of epidemics of control fraud,"},{"time":208604,"text":"particularly using this recipe."},{"time":211095,"text":"So let's go to this crisis,"},{"time":213002,"text":"and the two huge epidemics"},{"time":215851,"text":"of loan origination fraud that drove the crisis --"},{"time":219515,"text":"appraisal fraud and liar's loans --"},{"time":222348,"text":"and what we're going to see"},{"time":223793,"text":"in looking at both of these is"},{"time":226140,"text":"we got warnings that were incredibly early"},{"time":229393,"text":"about these frauds."},{"time":231362,"text":"We got warnings that we could\nhave taken advantage of easily,"},{"time":235500,"text":"because back in the savings and loan debacle,"},{"time":237970,"text":"we had figured out how to respond"},{"time":240590,"text":"and prevent these crises."},{"time":242668,"text":"And three, the warnings were unambiguous."},{"time":245972,"text":"They were obvious that what was going on"},{"time":248541,"text":"was an epidemic of accounting control fraud building up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":253420,"text":"Let's take appraisal fraud first."},{"time":255193,"text":"This is simply where you inflate the value"},{"time":257901,"text":"of the home that is being pledged"},{"time":260630,"text":"as security for the loan."},{"time":263227,"text":"In 2000, the year 2000,"},{"time":266733,"text":"that is over a year before Enron fails, by the way,"},{"time":271067,"text":"the honest appraisers got together a formal petition"},{"time":275303,"text":"begging the federal government to act,"},{"time":278405,"text":"and the industry to act,"},{"time":280260,"text":"to stop this epidemic of appraisal fraud."},{"time":284069,"text":"And the appraisers explained how it was occurring,"},{"time":287373,"text":"that banks were demanding that appraisers"},{"time":291010,"text":"inflate the appraisal,"},{"time":292920,"text":"and that if the appraisers refused to do so,"},{"time":296221,"text":"they, the banks, would blacklist"},{"time":300077,"text":"honest appraisers"},{"time":302299,"text":"and refuse to use them."},{"time":304851,"text":"Now, we've seen this before"},{"time":307413,"text":"in the savings and loan debacle,"},{"time":308941,"text":"and we know that this kind of fraud"},{"time":310765,"text":"can only originate from the lenders,"},{"time":313361,"text":"and that no honest lender would ever inflate"},{"time":316405,"text":"the appraisal,"},{"time":317714,"text":"because it's the great protection against loss."},{"time":320810,"text":"So this was an incredibly early warning, 2000."},{"time":324441,"text":"It was something we'd seen before,"},{"time":326622,"text":"and it was completely unambiguous."},{"time":328861,"text":"This was an epidemic of accounting control fraud"},{"time":332253,"text":"led by the banks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333850,"text":"What about liar's loans?"},{"time":335523,"text":"Well, that warning actually comes earlier."},{"time":339372,"text":"The savings and loan debacle is basically"},{"time":342001,"text":"the early 1980s through 1993,"},{"time":345548,"text":"and in the midst of fighting that wave"},{"time":348303,"text":"of accounting control fraud,"},{"time":350970,"text":"in 1990, we found that a second front"},{"time":355158,"text":"of fraud was being started."},{"time":357203,"text":"And like all good financial frauds in America,"},{"time":359358,"text":"it began in Orange County, California."},{"time":363210,"text":"And we happened to be the regional regulators for it."},{"time":366221,"text":"And our examiners said,"},{"time":368010,"text":"they are making loans without even checking"},{"time":371365,"text":"what the borrower's income is."},{"time":373868,"text":"This is insane, it has to lead to massive losses,"},{"time":378451,"text":"and it only makes sense for entities engaged"},{"time":382083,"text":"in these accounting control frauds."},{"time":384324,"text":"And we said, yeah, you're absolutely right,"},{"time":386595,"text":"and we drove those liar's loans"},{"time":389893,"text":"out of the industry in 1990 and 1991,"},{"time":394337,"text":"but we could only deal with the industry"},{"time":396389,"text":"we had jurisdiction over,"},{"time":398438,"text":"which was savings and loans,"},{"time":400143,"text":"and so the biggest and the baddest of the frauds,"},{"time":403523,"text":"Long Beach Savings, voluntarily gave up"},{"time":406429,"text":"its federal savings and loan charter,"},{"time":409298,"text":"gave up federal deposit insurance,"},{"time":411741,"text":"converted to become a mortgage bank"},{"time":414000,"text":"for the sole purpose of escaping our jurisdiction,"},{"time":417200,"text":"and changed its name to Ameriquest,"},{"time":419773,"text":"and became the most notorious"},{"time":421445,"text":"of the liar's loans frauds early on,"},{"time":425070,"text":"and to add to that,"},{"time":426606,"text":"they deliberately predated upon minorities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431826,"text":"So we knew again about this crisis."},{"time":435917,"text":"We'd seen it before. We'd stopped it before."},{"time":439151,"text":"We had incredibly early warnings of it,"},{"time":442341,"text":"and it was absolutely unambiguous"},{"time":444193,"text":"that no honest lender would\nmake loans in this fashion."},{"time":448399,"text":"So let's take a look at the reaction"},{"time":451241,"text":"of the industry and the regulators"},{"time":454187,"text":"and the prosecutors to these clear"},{"time":456990,"text":"early warnings that could have prevented the crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461457,"text":"Start with the industry."},{"time":463306,"text":"The industry responded between 2003 and 2006"},{"time":469260,"text":"by increasing liar's loans"},{"time":472101,"text":"by over 500 percent."},{"time":477333,"text":"These were the loans"},{"time":479228,"text":"that hyperinflated the bubble"},{"time":480983,"text":"and produced the economic crisis."},{"time":484631,"text":"By 2006, half of all the loans called subprime"},{"time":489482,"text":"were also liar's loans."},{"time":491508,"text":"They're not mutually exclusive, it's just that together,"},{"time":494793,"text":"they're the most toxic combination"},{"time":497233,"text":"you can possibly imagine."},{"time":499093,"text":"By 2006, 40 percent of all the loans"},{"time":502847,"text":"made that year, all the home loans made that year,"},{"time":505464,"text":"were liar's loans,"},{"time":508186,"text":"40 percent."},{"time":509497,"text":"And this is despite a warning"},{"time":512201,"text":"from the industry's own antifraud experts"},{"time":515624,"text":"that said that these loans were an open invitation"},{"time":518779,"text":"to fraudsters,"},{"time":520739,"text":"and that they had a fraud incidence"},{"time":522481,"text":"of 90 percent,"},{"time":524969,"text":"nine zero."},{"time":527661,"text":"In response to that, the industry"},{"time":530728,"text":"first started calling these loans liar's loans,"},{"time":535776,"text":"which lacks a certain subtlety,"},{"time":539345,"text":"and second, massively increased them,"},{"time":542395,"text":"and no government regulator ever"},{"time":545656,"text":"required or encouraged any lender"},{"time":549346,"text":"to make a liar's loan"},{"time":550642,"text":"or anyone to purchase a liar's loan,"},{"time":553329,"text":"and that explicitly includes Fannie and Freddie."},{"time":556499,"text":"This came from the lenders"},{"time":558621,"text":"because of the fraud recipe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561790,"text":"What happened to appraisal fraud?"},{"time":564224,"text":"It expanded remarkably as well."},{"time":567360,"text":"By 2007, when a survey of appraisers was done,"},{"time":571757,"text":"90 percent of appraisers reported"},{"time":574458,"text":"that they had been subject to coercion"},{"time":576898,"text":"from the lenders trying to get them"},{"time":579390,"text":"to inflate an appraisal."},{"time":580960,"text":"In other words, both forms of fraud"},{"time":583950,"text":"became absolutely endemic and normal,"},{"time":587724,"text":"and this is what drove the bubble."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589953,"text":"What happened in the governmental sector?"},{"time":592145,"text":"Well, the government, as I told you,"},{"time":594749,"text":"when we were the savings and loan regulators,"},{"time":597465,"text":"we could only deal with our industry,"},{"time":600143,"text":"and if people gave up their\nfederal deposit insurance,"},{"time":602581,"text":"we couldn't do anything to them."},{"time":604844,"text":"Congress, it may strike you as impossible,"},{"time":608173,"text":"but actually did something intelligent in 1994,"},{"time":611421,"text":"and passed the Home Ownership\nand Equity Protection Act"},{"time":614974,"text":"that gave the Fed, and only the Federal Reserve,"},{"time":618227,"text":"the explicit, statutory authority to ban liar's loans"},{"time":622254,"text":"by every lender,"},{"time":624360,"text":"whether or not they had federal deposit insurance."},{"time":627358,"text":"So what did Ben Bernanke and Alan Greenspan,"},{"time":630893,"text":"as chairs of the Fed, do"},{"time":632860,"text":"when they got these warnings"},{"time":634766,"text":"that these were massively fraudulent loans"},{"time":637776,"text":"and that they were being sold\nto the secondary market?"},{"time":641130,"text":"Remember, there's no fraud exorcist."},{"time":643350,"text":"Once it starts out a fraudulent loan,"},{"time":645398,"text":"it can only be sold to the secondary market"},{"time":647710,"text":"through more frauds,"},{"time":648906,"text":"lying about the reps and warrantees,"},{"time":651454,"text":"and then those people are going to produce"},{"time":653062,"text":"mortgage-backed securities"},{"time":654490,"text":"and exotic derivatives"},{"time":655758,"text":"which are also going to be supposedly backed"},{"time":658980,"text":"by those fraudulent loans."},{"time":660703,"text":"So the fraud is going to progress"},{"time":662244,"text":"through the entire system,"},{"time":663708,"text":"hyperinflate the bubble, produce a disaster."},{"time":666961,"text":"And remember, we had experience with this."},{"time":670262,"text":"We had seen significant losses,"},{"time":672550,"text":"and we had experience of competent regulators"},{"time":675996,"text":"in stopping it."},{"time":677486,"text":"Greenspan and Bernanke refused"},{"time":680382,"text":"to use the authority under the statute"},{"time":682793,"text":"to stop liar's loans."},{"time":685110,"text":"And this was a matter first of dogma."},{"time":687674,"text":"They're just horrifically opposed"},{"time":690525,"text":"to anything regulatory."},{"time":692344,"text":"But it is also the international competition in laxity,"},{"time":697060,"text":"the race to the bottom"},{"time":698344,"text":"between the United States and the United Kingdom,"},{"time":702379,"text":"the city of London, in particular,"},{"time":703980,"text":"and the city of London won that race to the bottom,"},{"time":706950,"text":"but it meant that all regulation in the West"},{"time":710802,"text":"was completely degraded"},{"time":712806,"text":"in this stupid competition to be"},{"time":714890,"text":"who could have the weakest regulation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":716962,"text":"So that was the regulatory response."},{"time":719012,"text":"What about the response of the prosecutors"},{"time":722669,"text":"after the crisis,"},{"time":724404,"text":"after 11 trillion dollars in losses,"},{"time":728602,"text":"after 10 million jobs lost,"},{"time":730642,"text":"a crisis in which the losses and the frauds"},{"time":733926,"text":"were more than 70 times larger"},{"time":737381,"text":"than the savings and loan debacle?"},{"time":739685,"text":"Well, in the savings and loan debacle,"},{"time":741576,"text":"our agency that regulated savings and loans, OTS,"},{"time":745546,"text":"made over 30,000 criminal referrals,"},{"time":749630,"text":"produced over 1,000 felony convictions"},{"time":752266,"text":"just in cases designated as major,"},{"time":754940,"text":"and that understates the degree of prioritization,"},{"time":758078,"text":"because we worked with the FBI"},{"time":759874,"text":"to create the list of the top 100 fraud schemes,"},{"time":764138,"text":"the absolute worst of the worst, nationwide."},{"time":767402,"text":"Roughly 300 savings and loans involved,"},{"time":770186,"text":"roughly 600 senior officials."},{"time":773500,"text":"Virtually all of them were prosecuted."},{"time":775840,"text":"We had a 90 percent conviction rate."},{"time":778671,"text":"It's the greatest success against"},{"time":780501,"text":"elite white collar criminals ever,"},{"time":783103,"text":"and it was because of this understanding"},{"time":785339,"text":"of control fraud"},{"time":786674,"text":"and the accounting control fraud mechanism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":789185,"text":"Flash forward to the current crisis."},{"time":792357,"text":"The same agency, Office of Thrift Supervision,"},{"time":794930,"text":"which was supposed to regulate"},{"time":796560,"text":"many of the largest makers of liar's loans"},{"time":798657,"text":"in the country,"},{"time":799764,"text":"has made, even today -- it no longer exists,"},{"time":804458,"text":"but as of a year ago,"},{"time":806266,"text":"it had made zero criminal referrals."},{"time":811110,"text":"The Office of the Comptroller of the Currency,"},{"time":812806,"text":"which is supposed to regulate\nthe largest national banks,"},{"time":815322,"text":"has made zero criminal referrals."},{"time":817873,"text":"The Fed appears to have made"},{"time":819499,"text":"zero criminal referrals."},{"time":821494,"text":"The Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation"},{"time":823449,"text":"is smart enough to refuse to answer the question."},{"time":827983,"text":"Without any guidance from the regulators,"},{"time":833518,"text":"there's no expertise in the FBI"},{"time":836400,"text":"to investigate complex frauds."},{"time":838872,"text":"It isn't simply that they've had"},{"time":840804,"text":"to reinvent the wheel"},{"time":842626,"text":"of how to do these prosecutions;"},{"time":844544,"text":"they've forgotten that the wheel exists,"},{"time":849300,"text":"and therefore, we have zero prosecutions,"},{"time":853398,"text":"and of course, zero convictions,"},{"time":856000,"text":"of any of the elite bank frauds,"},{"time":858790,"text":"the Wall Street types,"},{"time":860327,"text":"that drove this crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":863459,"text":"With no expertise coming from the regulators,"},{"time":865696,"text":"the FBI formed what it calls a partnership"},{"time":868787,"text":"with the Mortgage Bankers Association in 2007."},{"time":873110,"text":"The Mortgage Bankers Association"},{"time":874943,"text":"is the trade association of the perps."},{"time":878694,"text":"And the Mortgage Bankers Association"},{"time":881110,"text":"set out, it had the audacity and the success"},{"time":884900,"text":"to con the FBI."},{"time":886578,"text":"It had created a supposed definition"},{"time":889655,"text":"of mortgage fraud, in which, guess what,"},{"time":892530,"text":"its members are always the victim"},{"time":894392,"text":"and never the perpetrators."},{"time":896409,"text":"And the FBI has bought this hook, line, sinker,"},{"time":900923,"text":"rod, reel and the boat they rode out in."},{"time":905004,"text":"And so the FBI,"},{"time":908060,"text":"under the leadership of an attorney general"},{"time":911158,"text":"who is African-American"},{"time":912332,"text":"and a president of the United\nStates who is African-American,"},{"time":914794,"text":"have adopted the Tea Party definition of the crisis,"},{"time":918294,"text":"in which it is the first virgin crisis in history,"},{"time":921776,"text":"conceived without sin in the executive ranks."},{"time":925454,"text":"And it's those oh-so-clever hairdressers"},{"time":928850,"text":"who were able to defraud the poor, pitiful banks,"},{"time":932068,"text":"who lack any financial sophistication."},{"time":934452,"text":"It is the silliest story you can conceive of,"},{"time":937810,"text":"and so they go and they prosecute the hairdressers,"},{"time":941711,"text":"and they leave the banksters alone entirely."},{"time":945890,"text":"And so, while lions are roaming the campsite,"},{"time":948800,"text":"the FBI is chasing mice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":952010,"text":"What do we need to do?"},{"time":953440,"text":"What can we do in all of this?"},{"time":955944,"text":"We need to change the perverse incentive structures"},{"time":959763,"text":"that produce these recurrent epidemics"},{"time":962759,"text":"of accounting control fraud"},{"time":964088,"text":"that are driving our crises."},{"time":966102,"text":"So we have to first get rid"},{"time":968990,"text":"of the systemically dangerous institutions."},{"time":971478,"text":"These are the so-called too-big-to-fail institutions."},{"time":974963,"text":"We need to shrink them to the point,"},{"time":977105,"text":"within the next five years,"},{"time":978700,"text":"that they no longer pose a systemic risk."},{"time":981435,"text":"Right now, they are ticking time bombs"},{"time":983572,"text":"that will cause a global crisis"},{"time":986915,"text":"as soon as the next one fails --"},{"time":989264,"text":"not if, when."},{"time":991060,"text":"Second thing we need to do is completely reform"},{"time":993971,"text":"modern executive and professional compensation,"},{"time":996963,"text":"which is what they use to suborn the appraisers."},{"time":1001306,"text":"Remember, they were pressuring the appraisers"},{"time":1003194,"text":"through the compensation system,"},{"time":1004976,"text":"trying to produce what we call a Gresham's dynamic,"},{"time":1007638,"text":"in which bad ethics drives good ethics"},{"time":1010217,"text":"out of the marketplace."},{"time":1011583,"text":"And they largely succeeded,"},{"time":1013519,"text":"which is how the fraud became endemic."},{"time":1016402,"text":"And the third thing that we need to do"},{"time":1019100,"text":"is deal with what we call the three D's:"},{"time":1021738,"text":"deregulation, desupervision,"},{"time":1024319,"text":"and the de facto decriminalization."},{"time":1028340,"text":"Because we can make"},{"time":1030437,"text":"all three of these changes, and if we do so,"},{"time":1034111,"text":"we can dramatically reduce"},{"time":1036920,"text":"how often we have a crisis"},{"time":1039112,"text":"and how severe those crises are."},{"time":1042739,"text":"That is not simply critical to our economy."},{"time":1045720,"text":"You can see what these crises do to inequality"},{"time":1049146,"text":"and what they do to our democracy."},{"time":1051466,"text":"They have produced crony capitalism,"},{"time":1054210,"text":"American-style,"},{"time":1055592,"text":"in which the largest financial institutions"},{"time":1058870,"text":"are the leading financial donors of both parties,"},{"time":1062514,"text":"and that's the reason why"},{"time":1064434,"text":"even after this crisis,"},{"time":1068409,"text":"70 times larger than the savings and loan crisis,"},{"time":1073694,"text":"we have no meaningful reforms"},{"time":1076548,"text":"in any of the three areas that I've talked about,"},{"time":1079922,"text":"other than banning liar's loans,"},{"time":1081714,"text":"which is good,"},{"time":1082790,"text":"but that's just one form of ammunition"},{"time":1085214,"text":"for this fraud weapon."},{"time":1086610,"text":"There are many forms of ammunition they can use."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1090591,"text":"That's why we need to learn"},{"time":1092342,"text":"what the bankers have learned:"},{"time":1094454,"text":"the recipe for the best way to rob a bank,"},{"time":1097877,"text":"so that we can stop that recipe,"},{"time":1100742,"text":"because our legislators,"},{"time":1102504,"text":"who are dependent on political contributions,"},{"time":1105194,"text":"will not do it on their own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1107388,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1109458,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}